    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Specially constructed rooms with walls desgined with such sound-absorbency that the interior is as close to total silence as possible. They are generally used for scientific experiments.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
